<div class="content" >




 <div id="ilearn">   
    <div id="d1"><%= link_to image_tag( 'ilearn_logo.png', :id => "ilearn_logo"), 'http://ilearnohio.org/', :target => 'blank' %></div>
	<div id="d2"><%= link_to image_tag( 'ilearn_search_banner.jpg', :id => "ilearn_search"), 'http://ilearnohio.org/catalog_hs/' %></div>
	<div id="d3">Search nearly 500 full courses at iLearnOhio.org<br /><span class="fees">AP courses <i>may</i> be without fee.</span></div>
 </div>
 
 
 <h2>Courses</h2>
Are you a teacher (maybe even retired) who has an idea for a course? Do you know of a credit-worthy activity in your area? Is there an e-course you've seen which may benefit Ohio students?

This is the place to share, discuss, and reach students.   
<div class="clear"></div>
<% @courses.each do |course| %>

<div class="course2">
	<%= image_tag( course.course_image.url.to_s, :class => "course_avatar") if course.course_image? %>
    <span class="course_title"><%= course.title %></span><br />
	Subject area: <%= course.subject.name %>
	<p><%= course.description %></p>
	
    <p><b>Notes:</b> <%= course.notes %></p>
    <%= link_to 'More', course %> 
	<%= link_to 'Course link', course.plan_url %>
    
	<% if can? :update, course %>
    <%= link_to 'Edit', edit_course_path(course) %>
    <%= link_to 'Destroy', course, confirm: 'Are you sure,?', method: :delete %>
	<% end %>
</div>
<% end %>

<%= link_to( 'New Course', new_course_path, :class => 'add_button') %>
<br />
<div class="clear"></div>

</div>